    <div class="p-5 max-w-lg bg-slate-100 rounded-2xl shadow-md border-slate-200 m-auto group hover:bg-sky-800">
      <h1 class="text-black pt-5 text-[20px] font-semibold group-hover:text-white selection:bg-amber-300 selection:text-black">My Card</h1>
      <p class="first-line:text-cyan-500 first-letter:text-5xl first-letter:float-left first-letter:mr-1 group-hover:text-white selection:bg-amber-300 selection:text-black">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Illo ducimus deleniti iste iure architecto tempore amet accusamus sed officiis ipsam nihil officia, accusantium velit aliquid recusandae, animi dolore molestias excepturi?</p>
